						<summary>

						<p>On the bank of the well called <hi rend="italic">Huṇasimarada-bhāvi.</hi></p>						

						<p>1509-10 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated [Śaka] 1431, Śukla, Kārttika ba., the other details being lost. The Śaka year corresponds to 1509-10 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift of land to the deity Basava by a <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara.</hi></p>						

